{"tid":1033690,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"非洲博茨瓦納 倡撤獵象禁令 以生產寵物糧「大象肉罐頭」 (17:15)","createTime":"2019-02-23T11:10:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-23T11:10:11.000Z","uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"f1a8296a50467d878c667f415979269d1c568396","tid":1033690,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-23T11:10:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20190223/s00005/0007972cc8ac86e832c2156b27087fc2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20190223%2Fs00005%2F0007972cc8ac86e832c2156b27087fc2.jpg&h=07cfd8ce&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n圖1之1 - 非洲博茨瓦納野生動物保護區。（法新社圖片）<br />\n <br />\n非洲南部博茨瓦納約有13萬隻大象，數量佔非洲三分之一，被形容為非洲大象的最後保護區。博茨瓦納內閣部長於當地時間21日提交報告，建議政府取消已實施4年的狩獵大象禁令，並允許製作餵飼寵物的「大象肉罐頭」。<br />\n<br />\n總統馬西西（Mokgweetsi Masisi）去年上台後，要求內閣重新檢視於2014年頒布的大象獵捕禁令。報告亦建議，取消狩獵大象禁令、允許以象肉製作寵物飼料罐頭、定期有限地選擇性宰殺大象，以及制定法律框架以擴大野生動物狩獵業等。<br />\n<br />\n有國會議員認為，大象的實際數量比估計更多，大象活動範圍逐漸變大，踏入農村地區時容易破壞農田。但有保育人士認為，自政府頒布狩獵大象禁令後，能振興當地的旅遊觀光業。<br />\n<br />\n（CNN/路透社）<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B/article/20190223/s00005/1550912865880/%E9%9D%9E%E6%B4%B2%E5%8D%9A%E8%8C%A8%E7%93%A6%E7%B4%8D%E5%80%A1%E6%92%A4%E7%8D%B5%E8%B1%A1%E7%A6%81%E4%BB%A4-%E5%80%A1%E7%94%9F%E7%94%A2%E5%AF%B5%E7%89%A9%E7%B3%A7%E3%80%8C%E5%A4%A7%E8%B1%A1%E8%82%89%E7%BD%90%E9%A0%AD%E3%80%8D\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25E5%259C%258B%25E9%259A%259B%2Farticle%2F20190223%2Fs00005%2F1550912865880%2F%25E9%259D%259E%25E6%25B4%25B2%25E5%258D%259A%25E8%258C%25A8%25E7%2593%25A6%25E7%25B4%258D%25E5%2580%25A1%25E6%2592%25A4%25E7%258D%25B5%25E8%25B1%25A1%25E7%25A6%2581%25E4%25BB%25A4-%25E5%2580%25A1%25E7%2594%259F%25E7%2594%25A2%25E5%25AF%25B5%25E7%2589%25A9%25E7%25B3%25A7%25E3%2580%258C%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E8%25B1%25A1%25E8%2582%2589%25E7%25BD%2590%25E9%25A0%25AD%25E3%2580%258D&d=gMg1FBwAZA1XbJy1Uvmn1CLuFcS90NLYcDmgyrq2hhY%3D&h=74e00461\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25E5%259C%258B%25E9%259A%259B%2Farticle%2F20190223%2Fs00005%2F1550912865880%2F%25E9%259D%259E%25E6%25B4%25B2%25E5%258D%259A%25E8%258C%25A8%25E7%2593%25A6%25E7%25B4%258D%25E5%2580%25A1%25E6%2592%25A4%25E7%258D%25B5%25E8%25B1%25A1%25E7%25A6%2581%25E4%25BB%25A4-%25E5%2580%25A1%25E7%2594%259F%25E7%2594%25A2%25E5%25AF%25B5%25E7%2589%25A9%25E7%25B3%25A7%25E3%2580%258C%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E8%25B1%25A1%25E8%2582%2589%25E7%25BD%2590%25E9%25A0%25AD%25E3%2580%258D&h=9c78c5d2\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B/article/20190223/s00005/1550912865880/%E9%9D%9E%E6%B4%B2%E5%8D%9A%E8%8C%A8%E7%93%A6%E7%B4%8D%E5%80%A1%E6%92%A4%E7%8D%B5%E8%B1%A1%E7%A6%81%E4%BB%A4-%E5%80%A1%E7%94%9F%E7%94%A2%E5%AF%B5%E7%89%A9%E7%B3%A7%E3%80%8C%E5%A4%A7%E8%B1%A1%E8%82%89%E7%BD%90%E9%A0%AD%E3%80%8D</a>"}]}